quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,Did you not see/understand how (what) your Lord made/did with the elephant`s owners/company/ friends
  105,2,Did He not make their plotting/conspiring in misguidance
  105,3,And He sent on them flying/birds (in) flocks/groups gathered and following each other
  105,4,It throws them with stones from dry and hardened mud
  105,5,So He made them like eaten husk/chaff/leaves